      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pablo Vazquez</b>\n</p><p><b>Pablo Vazquez</b>,<br />\na Spanish computer chess programmer and author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> <a href=\"/Sungorus\" title=\"Sungorus\">Sungorus</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pablo_Vazquez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=21194\">Crafty questions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 16, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22755\">Sorting captures</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/MVV-LVA\" title=\"MVV-LVA\">MVV/LVA</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28490\">Sungorus 1.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28652\">Transposition Table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 26, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=29018\">SEE and en passant</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 19, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35217\">Sungorus 1.4</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pablo Vazquez</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 30, 2010</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pablo_Vazquez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/sungorus/\">Sungorus 1.4 - download</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pablo_Vazquez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/sungorus/\">Sungorus 1.4 - download</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152136\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: fals